Presenting “SKI PATROL”
This fine art limited edition print is a portrait of the ultimate alpine lady who refuses to let the cold deter her from a bare legged descent wearing her customized Louboutin skiis. She navigates the steep terrain with grace and elegance while keeping a watchful eye on the less hardy skiers than herself.
